data.description: Beautiful one level brick home with high quality Hardie siding in its exterior. Great spacious front yard and backyard, great overall leveled lot for your family to enjoy. Located in a really nice and quiet neighborhood and subdivision. Easy access to 1-75 and super close by Valley Point Middle and Elementary schools for your kids. The inside features flat ceilings with recessed lights throughout the home, commercial class A insulation in the attic! Water heater has new lines and valves. The garage features: epoxy on the floor, insulation in all walls, and recessed lighting. Schedule your private showing and come see this higher quality home!
